Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.19,0:00:10.15,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}When I was a kid,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.24,0:00:15.11,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I was always curious about the\Npeople beyond the valley fog.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.41,0:00:20.45,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}They always showed up before the summer rainy season,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.00,0:00:24.83,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}and vanished from the mountains by\Nthe time the storms had passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.14,0:00:48.11,ep-title-bg,,0,0,0,,{\fad(2100,2100)\p1\blur1}m 0 0 l 950 0 950 100 0 100
Dialogue: 1,0:00:40.14,0:00:48.11,ep-title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(2100,2100)\be1}The Sound of Footsteps on the Grass
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.22,0:00:59.72,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.72,0:01:03.14,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew you'd be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.48,0:01:05.79,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your father's calling.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.44,0:01:07.23,dialogue,,0,0,0,,'kay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.57,0:01:19.76,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a pretty purple today.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.66,0:01:24.48,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It only looks white to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.60,0:01:29.98,title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(816.19,121.905)\fad(2000,0)\p1\blur1\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&\3c&HFFFFFF&\3a&H00&\bord10\clip(676,67,956,177)\shad0}m 0 0 l 300 0 300 100 0 100
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.60,0:01:29.98,title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(814.857,120.906)\fad(2000,0)}Mushishi
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.95,0:01:27.17,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You sure are a strange child.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.94,0:01:34.19,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.61,0:01:38.16,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's already that time that they show up, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.49,0:01:40.49,dialogue,,0,0,0,,We gotta fix the windows.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.58,0:01:43.91,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you sure, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.33,0:01:46.41,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're just going to let them do\Nwhatever in our mountains?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.87,0:01:49.83,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's fine, they wouldn't do any harm.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.58,0:01:52.67,dialogue,,0,0,0,,They've been coming here for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.80,0:01:55.92,dialogue,,0,0,0,,They even hang out with the mountain patrollers.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.01,0:02:00.26,dialogue,,0,0,0,,What exactly do they do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.80,0:02:04.06,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know what they do for a living.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.77,0:02:08.10,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But they don't seem to be beggars.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.52,0:02:11.06,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I never got to know them that well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.48,0:02:15.23,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard they know a lot about different places,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.57,0:02:17.95,dialogue,,0,0,0,,and that they've always got interesting stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.36,0:02:21.07,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it's hard to know who they are, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.99,0:02:25.58,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those people might take the basin water.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.95,0:02:29.04,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, they're just travelers and it's just water.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.33,0:02:32.29,dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're not like the villagers who\Nwanted to send it to their crops.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.67,0:02:37.13,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I don't like it when outsiders go near there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.46,0:02:42.18,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Taku, you're going to be running our business,\Naren't you? Don't be so stingy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.05,0:02:45.89,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Think of them as passing birds.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.43,0:02:48.23,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just let them be.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.74,0:03:05.91,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, catch any?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.99,0:03:09.08,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The fish can see you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.25,0:03:15.38,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't take so many fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.05,0:03:18.38,dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is my mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.63,0:03:20.55,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.59,0:03:23.34,dialogue,,0,0,0,,So are you the Master here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.93,0:03:25.43,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm the Master's son.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.98,0:03:33.23,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Master's son?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.23,0:03:36.19,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.65,0:03:39.15,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Although I'm just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.49,0:03:41.11,dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're hungry too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.82,0:03:44.41,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could you spare us one each?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.66,0:03:48.79,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.37,0:03:51.04,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.37,0:03:53.42,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll give the rest back to the Master then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.71,0:03:57.21,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Isaza of Watari.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.75,0:04:01.01,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll be here for a while this year\Ntoo, so I'll see you around.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.22,0:04:03.80,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're an odd one, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.34,0:04:07.01,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're the Master's son and you suck at fishing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.22,0:04:12.60,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh my, that's a big catch.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.10,0:04:14.77,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Should we boil them or grill them?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.85,0:04:16.90,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's his problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.48,0:04:20.99,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's not like every mountain owner's\Nkid is good at fishing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.29,0:04:39.25,dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're all over the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.92,0:04:44.84,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you! You liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.47,0:04:46.84,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard from Grandpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.30,0:04:50.18,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You aren't the Master's son.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.47,0:04:51.68,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not a liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.97,0:04:55.44,dialogue,,0,0,0,,My ancestors spent a long time buying this mountain!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.77,0:04:57.94,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You bought it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.52,0:05:01.78,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you think you're the Master now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.23,0:05:05.20,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't just do anything you want here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.82,0:05:07.37,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not just doing anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.32,0:05:10.16,dialogue,,0,0,0,,This mountain's special, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.62,0:05:13.54,dialogue,,0,0,0,,This mountain's the reason the land here is so rich.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.04,0:05:16.92,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why my familiy's been protecting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.88,0:05:19.29,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad's the one stopping
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.29,0:05:22.59,dialogue,,0,0,0,,the townspeople from damming the waterfall and carrying the water to the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.55,0:05:27.80,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did a Mushi-shi tell you to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.84,0:05:31.56,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.51,0:05:34.93,dialogue,,0,0,0,,They told our ancestors.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.43,0:05:37.77,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or the mountain would get sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.98,0:05:40.15,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.48,0:05:44.53,dialogue,,0,0,0,,So it's precious to you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.20,0:05:48.49,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, fine then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.66,0:05:52.20,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was going to get you to pay for that fish from yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.33,0:05:53.37,dialogue,,0,0,0,,My bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.37,0:05:55.12,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.79,0:05:56.54,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.12,0:06:00.92,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll pay you back if you gave them to me by mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.59,0:06:04.05,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't need your charity.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.51,0:06:09.26,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.64,0:06:12.01,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.93,0:06:15.47,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I already got today's catch. Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.64,0:06:17.27,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I said hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.40,0:06:20.02,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.69,0:06:23.48,dialogue,,0,0,0,,that "Master" you talked about, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.07,0:06:27.11,dialogue,,0,0,0,,A huge catfish in this basin, apparently.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.57,0:06:30.36,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who decided that's the Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.70,0:06:33.20,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.58,0:06:37.37,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Master is born with grass on its body.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.08,0:06:39.75,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the marker.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.04,0:06:47.88,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've seen it before! It's a huge\Ncatfish with grass on its head.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.17,0:06:50.13,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really? Nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.30,0:06:51.51,dialogue,,0,0,0,,So hey,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.30,0:06:57.35,dialogue,,0,0,0,,have you seen the fog change\Ncolor and twist like it's alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.35,0:06:58.68,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.06,0:07:01.35,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a Koumyakusuji here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.06,0:07:07.15,notes,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,0)}Koumyakusuji: Koumyaku channel
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.61,0:07:07.15,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The source of life flows through this land.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.24,0:07:14.53,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It mixes with the water and evaporates\Nand turns into fog.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.70,0:07:16.66,dialogue,,0,0,0,,So the fog here is alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.54,0:07:22.42,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why it looks different depending on the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.34,0:07:27.13,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can tell how well the land is by looking at it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.22,0:07:34.97,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry, hurry! Stay calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.10,0:07:36.31,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.97,0:07:40.27,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not quite enough, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.60,0:07:41.31,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.73,0:07:47.48,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told you a lot of stuff that I know,\Nso now it's your turn to tell me stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.32,0:07:51.03,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't really know anything special.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.28,0:07:52.78,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tell me normal stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.24,0:07:57.99,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want to hear about what happens in the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.80,0:08:12.05,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Taku-bocchan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.17,0:08:14.72,dialogue,,0,0,0,,What brings you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.30,0:08:18.89,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wanted to hear some interesting stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.14,0:08:20.68,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, you're in luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.81,0:08:24.40,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was telling the chief about my travels.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.48,0:08:25.94,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.57,0:08:30.94,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that for real?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.49,0:08:32.36,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.70,0:08:35.53,dialogue,,0,0,0,,My uncle always exaggerates a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.49,0:08:38.58,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.37,0:08:42.87,dialogue,,0,0,0,,He saw a strange kid two mountains down south.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.00,0:08:47.38,dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's about ten years old, white hair, green eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.54,0:08:49.29,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And he only has one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.05,0:08:51.13,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.76,0:08:53.84,dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is he, a foreigner?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.38,0:08:56.26,dialogue,,0,0,0,,He says he didn't seem like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.64,0:09:00.51,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Two mountains down south, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.02,0:09:04.19,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the same route we go. Maybe I'll see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.77,0:09:09.19,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, the rainy season's over soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.57,0:09:10.61,dialogue,,0,0,0,,When are you leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.53,0:09:12.48,dialogue,,0,0,0,,No idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.11,0:09:15.53,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Grandpa looks at the fog every morning and decides.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.24,0:09:19.16,dialogue,,0,0,0,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.70,0:09:23.54,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The mountain's energy is settled\Nwhen there's a blue tint.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.91,0:09:25.66,dialogue,,0,0,0,,When it's reddish, it's the opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.21,0:09:31.17,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And when it's gold, the mountain's in a good\Nmood, so it's a good time to set out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.26,0:09:35.26,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sounds so carefree.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.76,0:09:41.18,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you jealous?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.01,0:09:44.48,dialogue,,0,0,0,,My whole future is set.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.73,0:09:49.98,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going to live fighting over the mountain like Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.57,0:09:52.65,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.83,0:10:13.71,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a map of the Koumyakusuji's\Ncourse over the past few years.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.09,0:10:17.47,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah. I'll have that map then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.76,0:10:18.93,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.26,0:10:20.26,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Isaza.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.68,0:10:23.47,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks for that "rumor" of yours. It came in handy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.81,0:10:25.98,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll ask you again sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.23,0:10:27.18,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.36,0:10:34.27,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what we do for a living.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.98,0:10:40.66,dialogue,,0,0,0,,We sell Mushi-shi information about potential\NMushi cases and Koumyakusuji changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.87,0:10:44.41,dialogue,,0,0,0,,No one would keep us fed if we just wandered around.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.95,0:10:48.91,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You could've told me earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.75,0:10:52.25,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then I would have listened for more suspicious stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.29,0:10:55.50,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That wouldn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.88,0:11:01.22,dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I didn't know what's normal in the village,\NI wouldn't know what's odd about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.64,0:11:04.43,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Plus I like hearing about the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.35,0:11:09.18,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.85,0:11:11.27,dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, "forget it"?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.31,0:11:13.73,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I get it, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.52,0:11:15.98,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're still pissed, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.36,0:11:17.99,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut up, quit following me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.07,0:11:23.99,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not apologizing. This is how I do things.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.58,0:11:26.20,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I never asked you to.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.00,0:11:38.01,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It flashed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.63,0:11:45.55,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The rainy season's finally over after this storm, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.54,0:12:13.04,dialogue,,0,0,0,,So hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.05,0:12:21.76,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isaza?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.51,0:12:29.64,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.07,0:12:41.07,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And next year,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.53,0:12:48.37,dialogue,,0,0,0,,they showed up at the same time of the year.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.04,0:12:56.00,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it wasn't the same gang of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.00,0:12:59.25,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we adopted him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.67,0:13:02.42,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was true what you told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.09,0:13:06.14,dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was wandering around town; said\Nhe didn't have anywhere to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.05,0:13:09.43,dialogue,,0,0,0,,He looks a bit odd, but he's cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.97,0:13:11.18,dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name's Ginko.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.72,0:13:13.14,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.14,0:13:17.44,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he probably won't be with us for long.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.44,0:13:20.36,dialogue,,0,0,0,,He tends to attract Mushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.40,0:13:23.49,dialogue,,0,0,0,,He can't stay by the Koumyakusuji for too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.69,0:13:26.86,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Either he or the Koumyaku would get hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.87,0:13:31.62,dialogue,,0,0,0,,He'll probably get handed over to a Mushi-shi soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.62,0:13:37.25,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fumi, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.75,0:13:38.88,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sir,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.92,0:13:43.09,dialogue,,0,0,0,,your father...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.76,0:13:49.68,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it says in his will that the whole\Nmountain goes to Taku.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.93,0:13:52.93,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I understand, but Aunt,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.39,0:13:55.85,dialogue,,0,0,0,,do you think Taku can play the right cards by himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.93,0:14:00.40,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The village is overcrowded; they need water.\NWe need to carry water somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.90,0:14:04.94,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, just leave it to us. We'll take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.25,0:14:16.87,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Taku.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.88,0:14:23.00,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Taku.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.42,0:14:29.13,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard from the patrollers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.18,0:14:33.14,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your dad... Sorry to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.18,0:14:36.27,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You haven't come out to the mountains lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.14,0:14:38.64,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.98,0:14:44.15,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't protect the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.73,0:14:48.03,dialogue,,0,0,0,,My relatives took it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.53,0:14:54.16,dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're going to dam the waterfall\Nand ruin the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.20,0:14:56.00,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.41,0:15:00.67,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Taku, listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.21,0:15:02.50,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something's wrong with the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.21,0:15:05.21,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's really upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.01,0:15:08.59,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The ground's hot and it smells weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.63,0:15:12.97,dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's less animals and the Koumyaku is shifting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.39,0:15:17.43,dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're going to move too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.18,0:15:19.94,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You guys be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.27,0:15:23.15,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you never coming here anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.73,0:15:26.98,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.36,0:15:35.16,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, let me in your group.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.29,0:15:38.87,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't want to be here anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.96,0:15:44.54,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Take me like that Ginko guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.75,0:15:47.80,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can see the fog's color too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.09,0:15:50.42,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't have to be related to you, do I?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.93,0:15:55.10,dialogue,,0,0,0,,None of us are related by blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.89,0:15:58.89,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Grandpa decides whether to take people or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.02,0:16:02.27,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll ask him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.10,0:16:05.02,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come to the waterfall tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.54,0:16:24.29,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The fog's plain white.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.21,0:16:27.67,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Something really is wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.67,0:16:30.76,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This never happened before.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.81,0:16:43.27,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where's Isaza?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.56,0:16:44.85,dialogue,,0,0,0,,He already left.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.69,0:16:47.81,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Liar. He...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.40,0:16:52.32,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Koumyaku started moving overnight.\NThey had no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.78,0:16:57.57,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isaza told me to tell you he said "sorry".
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.16,0:17:03.04,dialogue,,0,0,0,,They can't go against the Koumyaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.12,0:17:10.59,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Watari is a place where people gather when they\Nget driven out of their homes by Mushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.13,0:17:14.30,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You did too; you'll see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.51,0:17:18.68,dialogue,,0,0,0,,People like you, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.43,0:17:20.60,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.14,0:17:23.14,dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.10,0:17:27.81,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I lost my work again, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.31,0:17:31.19,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, one more thing he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.44,0:17:36.70,dialogue,,0,0,0,,"You guys should leave too."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.83,0:17:44.71,dialogue,,0,0,0,,From that day on, the mountain's\Nfog never took on a color.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.25,0:17:52.71,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And six months later...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.39,0:18:03.77,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The mountain spewed fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.52,0:18:08.40,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those who had a place to go went.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.15,0:18:15.03,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The mountain burned and the waterfall dried up,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.57,0:18:17.95,dialogue,,0,0,0,,but the basin remained in the form of a swamp.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.28,0:18:24.12,dialogue,,0,0,0,,One day, I saw the shadow of a huge catfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.83,0:18:31.50,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the grass that was once on its head wasn't there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.00,0:18:35.55,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Over the next ten-some years,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.47,0:18:42.05,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I shoveled ash and planted trees.\NThe mountain slowly revived,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.47,0:18:44.60,dialogue,,0,0,0,,but it never returned to its former vitality.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.98,0:18:51.81,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Many children were born frail.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.11,0:19:01.24,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isaza would have had some ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.12,0:19:04.28,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It must have something to do with the Koumyaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.95,0:19:09.29,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But what exactly was I to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.17,0:19:14.29,dialogue,,0,0,0,,How was I supposed to even find him?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.55,0:19:20.18,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even now, I jump when I hear the sound\Nof someone stepping through grass.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.34,0:19:24.60,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I keep thinking that they might have come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.23,0:19:31.10,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Taku!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.27,0:19:33.98,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Taku, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.57,0:19:38.07,dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's someone in the village\Nwho says he can cure the kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.95,0:19:44.53,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now keep making this drug like we just did,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.37,0:19:48.29,dialogue,,0,0,0,,and give him one dose each day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.04,0:19:51.29,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.58,0:19:57.80,dialogue,,0,0,0,,This land used to be a Koumyakusuji,\Nbut it got abandoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.34,0:20:02.30,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Many of the Mushi migrated along with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.51,0:20:05.30,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Only the ones that coexist with humans remained.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.39,0:20:10.81,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that why the kids are so weak?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.14,0:20:14.06,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow, you sure know a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.61,0:20:15.52,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's about right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.44,0:20:20.44,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You guys were born with the Koumyaku's blessings.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.82,0:20:21.95,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But not the kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.99,0:20:24.99,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I gave them nutrients and Mushi repellents.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.70,0:20:27.16,dialogue,,0,0,0,,They'll need it for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.08,0:20:29.08,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.46,0:20:32.67,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.00,0:20:36.79,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't seem to remember, but I've met you before.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.59,0:20:41.26,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah? Sorry, I can't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.26,0:20:44.55,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you remember Isaza?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.89,0:20:48.10,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.64,0:20:50.81,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm still good friends with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.85,0:20:54.35,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I came here because he told me about this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.60,0:20:59.36,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Said it's about time you'll be needing medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.03,0:21:01.65,dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's still at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.20,0:21:09.12,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.24,0:21:11.75,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's good then.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.08,0:21:16.00,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.01,0:21:31.68,dialogue,,0,0,0,,This huge catfish, the shape of this swamp...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.77,0:21:36.60,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've been here before.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.11,0:21:39.36,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.86,0:21:40.94,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.90,0:21:45.74,dialogue,,0,0,0,,He and the mountain sure have changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.16,0:21:48.41,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you think,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.58,0:21:52.83,dialogue,,0,0,0,,ex-Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.97,0:23:34.64,next-title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(870.857,256)\fad(0,2300)\be1\frz15.38}The\NSound\Nof\NFootsteps\Non the\NGrass
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.38,0:23:34.43,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The World is filled with life unknown to man.
